"title": "6121: boasting",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6121: boasting",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Negatively, conceitedly praising oneself. Positively, trusting and exulting in who God is, and what he has done.</p>\n<h2>Boasting condemned</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:16\">1JN 2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2-Ps10:6\">PSA 10:2–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:3-Ps12:4\">PSA 12:3–12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:1\">PSA 52:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:4\">PSA 94:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:10-Hab1:11\">HAB 1:10–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:29-Rom1:30\">ROM 1:29–1:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:2\">2TI 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Boasting exposed as folly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:1\">PRO 27:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:38-Judg9:40\">JDG 9:38–9:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:14\">PRO 25:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:18-1Cor3:23\">1CO 3:18–3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:16\">JAS 4:13–4:16</a></p>\n<h2>Salvation by faith means no-one can boast about human merit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:17-Rom2:24\">ROM 2:17–2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:27\">ROM 3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17-Rom11:21\">ROM 11:17–11:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:14\">GAL 6:14</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of foolish boasting</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:12-Isa10:14\">ISA 10:12–10:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:24-Isa37:25\">ISA 37:24–37:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:28-Dan4:30\">DAN 4:28–4:30</a> <em>Nebuchadnezzar</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:8\">DAN 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:11\">DAN 7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:36\">DAN 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:9-Acts8:10\">ACT 8:9–8:10</a> <em>Simon the sorcerer</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:4\">2TH 2:3–2:4</a> <em>the antichrist</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17-2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:17–2:18</a></p>\n<h2>Legitimate boasting</h2>\n<h3>Boasting in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1-1Sam2:3\">1SA 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:2\">PSA 34:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:8\">PSA 44:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:27-1Cor1:31\">1CO 1:27–1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:7-2Cor10:18\">2CO 10:7–10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:6\">HEB 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Boasting in the results of ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19-1Thess2:20\">1TH 2:19–2:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:17-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:17–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:31\">1CO 15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:24-2Cor9:3\">2CO 8:24–9:3</a></p>\n<h3>Boasting in the conduct of ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:12-2Cor1:14\">2CO 1:12–1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:15\">1CO 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:7-2Cor11:12\">2CO 11:7–11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10-2Tim3:11\">2TI 3:10–3:11</a></p>",
